<i>Posted by Tomiam Willowsong on 11-18-2002 08:12 AM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>One problem that was slowing this down when I got my flag, and thats people waiting until its their turn before starting to buff.  Then everyone is foced to wait for them to med.  Course.. the group that is behind them isnt ready either as they have just started buffing too.<br />
 Come on folks.. you know where you are in the list, at least start buffing so that you are ready when its your turn.   Yea, the ones in front could win, but with the failure rate being about 1 success to 10 or more failures (pure guess on what Ive seen) you got damn good odds of making sure you are ready.<br />
<br />
Tomiam Willowsong<br />
